    <tu tuid="shijing__song-minyuxiaozi-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">song-minyuxiaozi-005</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">載芟.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>載芟載柞，其耕澤澤。千耦其耘，徂隰徂畛。
侯主侯伯，侯亞侯旅，侯彊侯以。
有嗿其饁，思媚其婦，有依其士。
有略其耜，俶載南畝，播厥百穀，實函斯活。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>They clear away the grass and the bushes;
And the ground is laid open by their ploughs.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-minyuxiaozi-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">song-minyuxiaozi-005</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·005.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">載芟.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>驛驛其達，有厭其傑。厭厭其苗，緜緜其麃。
載穫濟濟，有實其積，萬億及秭。
為酒為醴，烝畀祖妣，以洽百禮，有飶其香，邦家之光。
有椒其馨，胡考之寧。匪且有且，匪今斯今，振古如茲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In thousands of pairs they remove the roots,
Some in the low wet land, some along the dykes.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
